OL,6,FFraud is having a lingering impact on
OL,7,Fsome victims' mental health, research
OL,8,Ffor Which? has found.
OL,10,FThe consumer group commissioned a
OL,11,Fsurvey of more than 1,000 people
OL,12,Facross the UK who had lost money to
OL,13,Ffraud in the last two years.
OL,15,FOf those who reported the fraud, just
OL,16,Fover half (55%) were able to get all
OL,17,Ftheir money back, but nearly a quarter
OL,18,F(22%) said they received no
OL,19,Freimbursement at all.
